# Unit 2: Lesson 10 - DNS in the Real World

## Background

DNS and IP address work in the real world because of the hierarchy and duplicity of DNS servers. The hierarchy of DNS/IP is analogous the system used by the postal service that includes country, state, city, zip, street, direction, number.

## Lesson

* Watch a video to learn about the hierarchy of DNS.
* Examine real-world issues related to DNS.
* Share your knowledge with your class through a jigsaw activity.

